'''森特理克'''（'''Centrica plc'''）是一家總部位英國[[伯克郡|伯克郡]][[溫莎_(伯克郡)|溫莎]]的跨國能源公司，主要業務為給英國和北美國家提供電力和天然氣，此外也有開採天然氣的業務。

==历史==
1997年创建，森特理克已在[[倫敦證券交易所|倫敦證券交易所]]上市，曾是[[富時100指數|富時100指數]]成分。{{as of|2014|12|23}}，該公司市值為150億英鎊，是倫敦證券交易所全部上市公司中的第37大公司。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.stockchallenge.co.uk/ftse.php| title=FTSE All-Share Index Ranking| publisher=stockchallenge.co.uk| accessdate=26 December 2011| archive-date=2012-03-10| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310231136/http://www.stockchallenge.co.uk/ftse.php| dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[2019冠状病毒病英国疫情|2019冠状病毒病英国疫情]]期间，大量公司办公室和工厂关闭，导致其股票暴跌至历史最低点£0.30<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/nils-pratley-on-finance/2020/apr/22/british-gas-owner-needs-more-than-cost-cutting-and-energy-prices-prayer|title=British Gas owner needs more than cost-cutting and energy prices prayer|author=Pratley|first=Nils|date=22 April 2020|website=|7=|access-date=23 April 2020|newspaper=The Guardian|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228230308/https://www.theguardian.com/business/nils-pratley-on-finance/2020/apr/22/british-gas-owner-needs-more-than-cost-cutting-and-energy-prices-prayer|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2020年6月，该公司从富時100指數除名，成为[[富時250指數|富時250指數]]成分股。当月，公司宣布裁员5,000人。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.ft.com/content/c5f4dca3-1f51-49fa-acd4-4fb88977e4e5|title=Centrica to shed 5,000 roles as UK job losses mount|work=[[Financial_Times|Financial Times]]|date=11 June 2020|accessdate=11 June 2020|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216073719/https://www.ft.com/content/c5f4dca3-1f51-49fa-acd4-4fb88977e4e5|dead-url=no}}</ref>

